.Sh ENTERPRISE REFACTOR ROADMAP
.Bl -tag -width "Phase 6"
.It Phase 1
Module attach API and router separation.
Complete: all modules use
.Fn miniweb_module_attach_enabled .
.It Phase 2
Single global heartbeat scheduler.
Complete: metrics and networking modules both run named heartbeat tasks.
.It Phase 3
Domain decomposition of metrics, networking, man, packages.
Ongoing.
.It Phase 4
Documentation and architecture transition (docs/miniweb.1 + README.md, module porting to enterprise paradigm).
In progress.
.It Phase 5
SQLite3 storage integration.
Stub interfaces are defined.
.It Phase 6
Performance and observability hardening.
Planned.
.El
